== 用法 ==
本模版用於河流的特徵，包含橋樑、島嶼、水閘等，具體例子可參見[[Template:River item box/examples|examples]]。 

;基本用法:
<pre>
{{River item box
|River = #
|upstream = #
|downstream = #
}}
</pre>

* 顯示有“#”的項目是必須要有的。

;高級用法:
<pre>
{{River item box
|River = #
|upstream = #
|downstream = #

|type = any text (defaults to crossing)
|thisis = any test (defaults to {{PAGENAME}})
|upsub = 
|downsub = 
|location = 

|table = see extended table below
|upstream2 = see River junction below
|upsub2 = see River junction below
}}
</pre>

* 顯示有“#” 的項目是必須要有的
* |River 需要首字大寫以便與其它模版兼容
* |type 和 |thisis have the defaults shown
* |location 僅用於英格蘭

==Using the correct template==
The template is designed as a one line replacement for [[Template:River bridge start]] and [[Template:River item line]]. It should also make the following redundant: [[Template:River island start]], [[Template:River bridge start]], [[Template:River bridge line]], [[Template:River item line X]].

==Extended table==
It is possible to generate a block of these templates using the option |table =. The first call uses |table = start; the middle ones |table = middle; and the final one |table = end. Beware: the alignment in the third column can be disrupted unless the templates are linked together with a comment e.g. &lt;!-- --> - [[Template:River item box/examples#Extended table|See examples]]. 

==River junction==
Where there is a river junction upstream the options |upstream2 = and |upsub2 = can be used. [[Template:River item box/examples#River junction|See examples]].

